msgid "Na kho panete, cunda, ariyassa vinaye sallekhā vuccanti. "
msgstr "But in the training of the noble one these are not called ‘self-effacement’; "

msgctxt "mn8:10.5"
msgid "Santā ete vihārā ariyassa vinaye vuccanti. "
msgstr "they’re called ‘peaceful meditations’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya11, pts-vp-pli1.42, sc10
msgctxt "mn8:11.1"
msgid "Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, cunda, vijjati yaṃ idhekacco bhikkhu sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja vihareyya. "
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, might enter and remain in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "

msgctxt "mn8:11.2"
msgid "Tassa evamassa: "
